The paper deals with autonomous UAV racing, which involves robotics and control (cs.RO). The approach involves learning from raw images, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV). The paper proposes using a DNN to learn a robust controller, which involves machine learning (cs.LG) and control systems (cs.SY). The approach involves fusing multiple controllers, which involves artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
